mun coc phang.json. Are flat warts dangerous?
Are not! Flat warts are caused by low-risk types of HPV virus, so they do not develop into other dangerous diseases. They only cause some unpleasant and unsightly symptoms, affecting the psychology of the person who encounters them, and are capable of infecting people around them.
